íŸ@b2b93fbd633da500d8c02c03fee7782317a19324012d66bf3b979e1106afc0bc⁄:Title: title: help aliases
Path: Examples
Content:
Show all aliases.
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> help aliases


```
Show help for single alias.
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> help aliases my-alias


```
Search for string in alias names and descriptions.
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> help aliases --find my-alias


```
